\v 16 \x - \xo 11:16 \xt Akar Mogomem 4:4; 4:10; 5:8; 19:4\x*EzÉØ 24plan gumazir dapanir GodÉØn guamÉØn uan atrivir dabirabibagh apiaziba, me teviba apÉØrigha uan guaba nguazim mÉØtuagha GodÉØn ziam fe.  
