\v 18 \x - \xo 11:18 \xt Onger Akaba 2:1; 2:5; 46:6; 110:5; 115:13; Daniel 7:9-10; Rom 2:5; Akar Mogomem 6:10; 10:7; 13:10; 18:6; 19:5; 20:11-13\x*Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bar puvÉØram atari, 
